import React from "react"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import { Image, Media } from "react-bootstrap"; import { translate, t } from "react-multi-lang"; const FanTabSec = (props) => { return (
    props.changeSection(event, "active-sec")} > {t("active")} props.changeSection(event, "expired-sec")} > {t("unsubscribed")} props.changeSection(event, "all-sec")} > {t("all")}
); }; export default translate(FanTabSec);
